description: Rare opportunity located in the most vibrant and coveted building in Seaport, The Echelon. Enjoy the most expansive 2 bed/2 bath floor plan w/ private outdoor space. This home offers extra sunlight and views of the courtyard and pools. Displaying floor-to-ceiling windows w/ custom blinds, modern kitchen w/ Italian flat panel cabinetry, a large island w/ Caesarstone quartz countertops, Thermador integrated appliances, millwork in primary, custom closets, white oak floors, and recessed lighting throughout. Enhanced by a detailed marble-appointed bathroom with custom vanity and double sinks. Enjoy the 5-star services that this full service building offers and amenities like no other building in the city- 50,000 sq/ft of common space! Use the private dining room, owners lounge, roof terrace, 3 pools (1 indoor, 2 outdoor), outdoor grills, fitness center, spa, indoor basketball court, golf simulator, and more! Including 1 Valet Parking plus 1 Rented Valet Parking Space, and Storage Unit.
